<div id="outline-container-ID-252f0dd2-3c62-4db4-9974-8fae8eebfe79" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="ID-252f0dd2-3c62-4db4-9974-8fae8eebfe79">Reading inbox</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org9395fe4">
<p>
A index of videos, books and other things that got my attention.
Not all might be read or watched.
</p>

<p>
Key:
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>TODO, YES means im going to read it</li>
<li>IDEA means i might do it may remove</li>
<li>KILL, NO means im not going to read it</li>
<li class="on"><code>[X]</code> means complete</li>
<li class="trans"><code>[-]</code> Means in progress</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

